  "prompt": "How do I remove a non-friend from Facebook messenger contact list?",
  "response": "Here's how to remove someone from Facebook Messenger:\n\n1. Open Facebook Messenger\n2. Find the conversation with that person\n3. Tap on their name at the top of the chat\n4. Scroll down and select \"Remove Conversation\"\n\nThis will delete the chat from your messenger. If you want to block the person completely:\n\n1. Go to their profile\n2. Click the \"...\" menu\n3. Select \"Block\"\n\nBlocking will prevent them from messaging or contacting you on Facebook.",
